| `app/Models/PaketBundlingModel.php` | **BARU** | CRUD + kalkulasi total harga normal, hemat, persen hemat |
| `app/Controllers/PaketBundling.php` | **BARU** | Controller lengkap (index/pending/cancelled/create/store/show/edit/update/activate/cancel/draft/restore/delete) |
| `app/Views/paket_bundling/index.php` | **BARU** | Daftar paket (kartu + badge "Hemat X%") |
| `app/Views/paket_bundling/create.php` | **BARU** | Form tambah paket + checklist menu + qty + kalkulator total (JS real-time) |
| `app/Views/paket_bundling/edit.php` | **BARU** | Form edit paket, menu terpilih otomatis tercentang |
| `app/Views/paket_bundling/detail.php` | **BARU** | Detail paket: isi paket, harga normal, harga paket, hemat |
